n- *construir* **y-insertion** (3rd indef.) â†’ **construyÃ³/construyeron**\n\n> ðŸ§  **C2 takeaway:** Generate forms by **deriving from rules** (sound â†’ spelling; stress â†’ vowel change) instead of rote lists.\n",
